# Tech Stack Document

## Technology Stack

| Layer | Library/Service | Version | Purpose | Documentation |
|-------|----------------|---------|---------|---------------|
| **Runtime** | Python | 3.11+ | Modern Python runtime with async support | [docs.python.org](https://docs.python.org/3/) |
| **Bot SDK** | python-telegram-bot | 21.0+ | Official Telegram Bot API wrapper with async support | [python-telegram-bot.org](https://docs.python-telegram-bot.org/) |
| **OpenAI SDK** | openai | 1.12+ | Official OpenAI API client for GPT-4 integration | [platform.openai.com/docs](https://platform.openai.com/docs/libraries/python-library) |
| **Database** | - | - | Not required for MVP | - |
| **Deployment** | Railway | - | Simple deployment platform with GitHub integration | [docs.railway.app](https://docs.railway.app/) |
| **Linter/Formatter** | Ruff | 0.1.0+ | Fast Python linter and formatter (replaces Black + Flake8) | [docs.astral.sh/ruff](https://docs.astral.sh/ruff/) |

## Additional Dependencies

| Dependency | Version | Purpose | Documentation |
|------------|---------|---------|---------------|
| **python-dotenv** | 1.0.0+ | Environment variables management | [pypi.org/project/python-dotenv](https://pypi.org/project/python-dotenv/) |
